title: Faahfaahinta Hantida
description: Nooga waran faahfaahinta gaarka ah ee hantiyeedkaaga
safetyInfoDescription: Astaamo badbaado oo caadi ah ayaa ku jira
weaponsOnProperty: Ma jiraan hub ku yaal hantiyeedka?
securityCameras: Ma jiraan kamarado amni oo hantiyeedka yaal?
minLengthWarning: Ugu yaraan {{min}} xaraf ayaa loo baahan yahay
tipContent: Baadh hantiyaal la mid ah deegaankaaga si aad u dejiso qiime tartan leh. Mar walba waad beddeli kartaa qiimahaaga hadba baahida.
